 - hoods too, and - we'd have a - a trip to - Trentham or - Barleston, for this ha'penny a week when we'd saved you know, and - there was a certain big house, somebody connected with the chapel, and - we'd go there and sing at this house and that was an o
ccasion. The ride you see used to be the thrill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1192360 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14292676\charrsid12133966 What other social activities organised by the chapel did you take part in?

