Prize distribution. That was once a year. You see, and we always got a good prize because - we had to be - good attenders you see. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1192360 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14292676\charrsid12133966 Did you belong to the choir?
